A '''completist''' is a [[collector]] who specifically tries to assemble a complete collection of something, owning one sample of each possible item in the collection.<ref>''Comics: Between the Panels''</ref>

For instance, a music collector might try to collect every song recorded by [[The White Stripes]]. Some [[comic book]] collectors attempt to buy every issue of a series or every issue in which a specific charatcer makes an appearance.

Upon completing a particular collection, a completist may stop collecting, expand the collection to include related items, or begin an entirely new collection.

